{"tid":140481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚悲歌　男子屍體被6噸重咸書包圍","createTime":"2017-03-02T08:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T05:42:39.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d85748fa7a418bdd92608f7510512afc0c11122f","tid":140481,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:20:10.000Z","msg":"2017年03月02日15:25<br />\n<br />\n（更新：新增影片）死了以後沒被人發現，被蟲當成食物吃掉的孤獨死死者，在這十年間增加了3倍左右，而這個孤獨死案例，則是房間堆滿了情色雜誌等物品，過了1個多月後才被發現。<br />\n<br />\n據《日刊SPA！》報導，這件孤獨死死者的房間，堆滿角落的都是成人錄影帶，色情雜誌則是堆到腰部一般高，這位在神奈川自動車公司上班的50多歲男性，就在這個被色情雜誌包圍的情況下過世，死因是心肌梗塞，已經死亡超過1個月以上。<br />\n<br />\n「說到孤獨死的話，亡者的房間大多有固定的模式，是男性的房間的話，大多就是像這樣沉浸在自己世界觀居多，想這間2DK的房間，色情雜誌就有6噸的份量。」輕描淡語說出這些話的，是從事特殊清掃一品整理業的鷹田了。他指出，孤獨死的人，大多都是有特殊興趣、性癖的宅宅，不過像這案例有大量成人用品的房間，還是讓他相當吃驚。<br />\n<br />\n「避免死者不想被看到的部分曝光，像是這種有情趣用品的房間，我們都會盡量在死者家屬知道前處理掉。」不幸中的大幸是，這房間因為散落大量的色情雜誌，恰好吸收了屍體溢出來的體液，沒有對樓下的住戶造成影響，一般來說，死後一個月，樓下都會佈滿屍體的體液，需要大筆修繕費用才能恢復。<br />\n<br />\n「也有住在樓下的房客，被體液給滴到頭後，才發現樓上的房客已經死亡的案例在」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170302/420_6d8e35252544f1b3d6f1f0dbfec3f938.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170302%2F420_6d8e35252544f1b3d6f1f0dbfec3f938.jpg&h=34f27956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170302/420_b3c0dbfcfab5aff5d28ac3bfa0cee139.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170302%2F420_b3c0dbfcfab5aff5d28ac3bfa0cee139.jpg&h=0d3ae858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孤獨死的房間，裡面有六噸的色情雜誌。翻攝自《日刊SPA！》"},{"pid":"54c53657d288e90a47fc41816ed8ba2007712445","tid":140481,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7723da72a9946fc8410bbbc023c219985301fb","tid":140481,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855b44f6a27364ae855c7b3e77d09152f9e3c226","tid":140481,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e004ec623e14c917b25cb0495e924ed5f80ef503","tid":140481,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:39:49.000Z","msg":"真係好撚慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18cb80ea3bfd833935ca02001c81a1b4302b26b","tid":140481,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409b4679aa60361cf3d5526ab7abbcd668f601df","tid":140481,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:02:15.000Z","msg":"對比呢個神級毒撚，自己真係咩都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9414f0a9ceb02ffc8799d4231b1a5758b085cd53","tid":140481,"uid":69987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"仲要毒死"},{"pid":"809c8aa9f2e5541b5c891c42c53b3846cf63cf04","tid":140481,"uid":88485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對比呢個神級毒撚，自己真係咩都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以為自己樣已經比唔上其他人，連做毒撚都輸俾人<br />\n學你話，自己真係咩都唔係"},{"pid":"096f3f57e5283760c7bbe67f4310a8d783d6b43c","tid":140481,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}